01:20:06,502 --> 01:20:06,603
I remember John Carter, who
won an Academy Award, by the way,

1455
01:20:06,618 --> 01:20:09,553
I remember John Carter, who
won an Academy Award, by the way,

1456
01:20:09,621 --> 01:20:12,306
for best sound for Jaws.

1457
01:20:12,891 --> 01:20:16,759
He picked up the Nagra
and held it over his head

