1499
01:22:10,426 --> 01:22:13,305
It weighs about 400 pounds.
It's very clumsy.

1500
01:22:13,429 --> 01:22:16,262
It does keep the camera level aboard ship,

1501
01:22:16,799 --> 01:22:21,487
but it's too clumsy to do a
film the way they do films today.

1502
01:22:22,171 --> 01:22:24,856
And so I chose to hand-hold the camera.

1503
01:22:25,374 --> 01:22:29,060
When Steven heard about this
he was rather shocked,

1504
01:22:29,178 --> 01:22:31,977
because he didn't really
want a hand-held picture.

1505
01:22:32,064 --> 01:22:35,443
But he didn't realize
that I didn't really mean

1506
01:22:35,551 --> 01:22:38,111
to do a hand-held film

1507
01:22:38,287 --> 01:22:41,803
in the terms that they
then used or thought about

1508
01:22:41,874 --> 01:22:43,342
hand-held on land,

1509
01:22:43,408 --> 01:22:45,172
but rather to use the knees

1510
01:22:45,244 --> 01:22:47,713
<i>and the body to take
the roll out of the film.</i>

1511
01:22:47,930 --> 01:22:52,561
<i>And so we gave that a try,
